I was honored to be apart of this film that documented his life. The trips were so so fun chasing the longest waves in the far corners of the world. 🌎🏄‍♂️

#thelongestwave #windsurfingdocumentary #windsurfing @joeberlingerfilms @chuckpatterson

It has been a great tool for helping me achieve my best! 💯 #ouraring
